data.description: Welcome home! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasts 2116 square feet, complete with a refreshing pool & spa and a spacious 2-car garage with oversized driveway providing ample parking. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the custom kitchen loaded with cabinet space– a culinary masterpiece that combines style and functionality seamlessly.  This gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, showcasing custom cabinetry, high-end SAMSUNG appliances, and exquisite countertops. Whether you're a culinary enthusiast or simply love to entertain, this kitchen is sure to be the heart of your home. Step into elegance as you explore the warm tones of the hardwood floors. The expansive master suite features a spacious walk in closet. Entertain effortlessly in the backyard paradise, where a sparkling pool invites you to relax and unwind. Take a dip in the refreshing pool or unwind in the spa, surrounded by lush landscaping for added privacy. The pool area becomes a tranquil retreat, perfect for relaxation and rejuvenation. Imagine hosting gatherings under the stars in your private outdoor haven. Enjoy the luxury of newer windows throughout the home, providing not only aesthetic appeal but also increased energy efficiency.  Situated in a desirable location, this home offers both tranquility and accessibility and is just a short 15 minute drive to some of the nation's best rated sugar sand beautiful beaches and world class dining & nightlife making this home a practical choice for families and individuals alike. For the sports enthusiast and fan, Tampa Bay's World Champion sports teams are within very close proximity. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional residence yours.
